ORDER
PER CURIAM.
And now, this 30th day of November, 2011 the Petition for Allowance of Appeal is hereby DENIED.
The Motion to Withdraw as Counsel filed by Attorney Barbara A. McDermott is hereby GRANTED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
